name: [V2]Artist: rurudo | rurudo artist's painting style
description:
rurudo Style LoRA

中文 | English 使用前阅读 | Read before use

--

仿rurudo的作画风格的LoRA模型。适合画双马尾萝莉。

权重建议值：1 (or 0.6~1.2)

基于模型：Anything-5RE

训练信息：共计130张原画（含裁剪图），最后一次训练迭代520步。

拟合比率：

  • 肢体拟合：12%

  • 人物拟合：78%

  • 构图拟合：30%

  • 技法拟合：102%

其他的一些建议：badhandv4, EasyNegative。

The LoRA model mimics Rurudo's painting style, which is suitable for drawing twin-tailed lolis.

Recommended weight value: 1 (or 0.5~1)

Based on model: Anything-5RE

Training information:

A total of 130 paintings (including cropped images) with 520 iterations.
Fitting ratio:

  • Motion fitting: 12%

  • Character fitting: 78%

  • Composition fitting: 30%

  • Technique fitting: 102%

Other suggestions: EasyNegative, badhandv4.

--

任何问题，欢迎反馈，问题不提出就不会得到解决。如果你创作出了好作品，欢迎分享它。如果它无法满足你的需求，我是说，我的朋友，请不要给出一星好评。

Any questions are welcome for feedback, as problems will not be solved without being raised. If you have created a great work, please feel free to share it. If it cannot meet your needs, my friend, please do not give a one-star rating.
